  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWatching our Prater validators, all blocks produced with Lodestar are orphaned:\r\n- https://prater.beaconcha.in/validator/200983#blocks (node with 1 validator)\r\n- https://prater.beaconcha.in/validator/200984#blocks (node with 16 validators)\r\n\r\nI tracked a missed block proposal in the REST API metrics and got:\r\n- produceBlock: 4.01s\r\n- publishBlock: 64.1ms\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nBlocks must be produced way faster. Otherwise we won't get attestations on it and the network will ignore it. Other clients produce blocks in ~ 100ms tops if I recall.\r\n\r\n- [ ] Add benchmark to produceBlock\r\n- [ ] Debug and improve performance",
