    "body": "the produceBlock itself may not be an issue as when I call that api in my server without any validator, it returned immediately.\r\n\r\na lot of apis takes ~4s as in http://167.86.102.209:3000/d/lodestar/lodestar?orgId=1&refresh=30s, for example `getAttesterDuties` or `produceAttestationData`\r\n\r\nwe need to improve out node in general, it's most likely it's the attestation gossip tasks as shown below from a node with full attestation subscriptions\r\n<img width=\"1301\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-06-24 at 15 05 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/123226284-b7c6b700-d4fd-11eb-8d11-11b1c2eac4c8.png\">\r\n[0624-prater-full-attestation-subscriptions.cpuprofile.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/6707467/0624-prater-full-attestation-subscriptions.cpuprofile.zip)\r\n",
